# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT REMINDERS
# ============================================================================
#
# NEVER COMMIT:
# - .env files (contain passwords and secrets)
# - Private keys (SSL, SSH, DKIM, GPG)
# - Database dumps with real data
# - Actual mail content
# - Production credentials
# - API tokens/keys
#
# ALWAYS COMMIT:
# - .env.example (template without secrets)
# - Documentation
# - Example configurations
# - Public keys (if needed)
# - Schema/structure files
#
# ============================================================================
